Module com.cateringfx
Package com.cateringfx.model

Class Aliment

java.lang.Object
com.cateringfx.model.MenuElement
com.cateringfx.model.Aliment
public class Aliment extends MenuElement

Define an Aliment by its attributes frequency, calories, carbohydrates, fat, milk, nuts, egg and gluten.

Extends from the abstract class MenuElement and implement its abstract methods: MenuElement.getCalories(), MenuElement.getCarbohydrates() , MenuElement.getFat(), MenuElement.isMilk(), MenuElement.isNuts(), MenuElement.isEgg() and MenuElement.isGluten().

Version:
1.0.
Author:
Francisco David Manzanedo Valle.
See Also:
MenuElement
